Geometrical setup is defined thru  AMSJob.Setupname datacard (see datacards.doc)


Rules & valid cards:

each (sub) detector entry is prefixed by 3 symbol detector abbreviation.

Valid prefixes:

AMS  - whole detector

TOF  - time of flight counter

ANT  - anti coincidence counter

STR  - silicon trackert

CTC  - threshold cerenkov counter

TRD  - transition radiation detector

PSH  - plastic shield + AMS support structure

CAL - emc

RIC - RICH



Valid entries (on  26/09/96)


AMS:
AMSSHUTTLE(Default)/AMS02       - shuttle/station 

STR:
STRPLANES(Default)/STRTUBES          -  planes/tubes   

CTC:
CTCHor(Default)/CTCVer/CTCSimple/CTCAnnecy/CTCNo   
  - horizontal/vertical/simplified/current  CTC readout/NoCTC


CALORIMETER:
CAL01

TRD:
TRD01



 
